{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/kubernetes/CKA/cka2/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CKA 시험 준비 1일차","date":"October 28, 2024"},"html":"<h1>CKA 시험 준비 1일차</h1>\n<p>일단 11월 25일에 <a href=\"https://training.linuxfoundation.org/certified-kubernetes-administrator-cka-program-changes/\">CKA가 바뀐다고 한다</a>. 그러면 내용이 어떻게 바뀔지 모르기 때문에 그 전에 최대한 한번 시도해보려고 한다.</p>\n<p>각오를 보이기 위해 시험 일정을 잡기로 했다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sched1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4a94b42d85987d2130ca19b9ee86e9ee/5a190/sched1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a94b42d85987d2130ca19b9ee86e9ee/772e8/sched1.png 200w,\n/static/4a94b42d85987d2130ca19b9ee86e9ee/e17e5/sched1.png 400w,\n/static/4a94b42d85987d2130ca19b9ee86e9ee/5a190/sched1.png 800w,\n/static/4a94b42d85987d2130ca19b9ee86e9ee/c1b63/sched1.png 1200w,\n/static/4a94b42d85987d2130ca19b9ee86e9ee/29007/sched1.png 1600w,\n/static/4a94b42d85987d2130ca19b9ee86e9ee/037ab/sched1.png 2274w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>시험 시간이 주중에는 새벽에만 가능하다. 어처피 봐야하는거 금요일 오전 6시에 봐야겠다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sched2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/501074ce901e8d8f284446bc9bc94dd2/5a190/sched2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/501074ce901e8d8f284446bc9bc94dd2/772e8/sched2.png 200w,\n/static/501074ce901e8d8f284446bc9bc94dd2/e17e5/sched2.png 400w,\n/static/501074ce901e8d8f284446bc9bc94dd2/5a190/sched2.png 800w,\n/static/501074ce901e8d8f284446bc9bc94dd2/c1b63/sched2.png 1200w,\n/static/501074ce901e8d8f284446bc9bc94dd2/29007/sched2.png 1600w,\n/static/501074ce901e8d8f284446bc9bc94dd2/809bc/sched2.png 2612w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>정확히 24일 남았다. 일부러 최대한 널널하게 잡았다. 오늘부터 다시 한번씩 매일 시험을 풀어볼 예정이다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 37%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"sched3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d0253630c08e797bed827cf46bbd1fa3/5a190/sched3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d0253630c08e797bed827cf46bbd1fa3/772e8/sched3.png 200w,\n/static/d0253630c08e797bed827cf46bbd1fa3/e17e5/sched3.png 400w,\n/static/d0253630c08e797bed827cf46bbd1fa3/5a190/sched3.png 800w,\n/static/d0253630c08e797bed827cf46bbd1fa3/c1b63/sched3.png 1200w,\n/static/d0253630c08e797bed827cf46bbd1fa3/29007/sched3.png 1600w,\n/static/d0253630c08e797bed827cf46bbd1fa3/5fc9a/sched3.png 1648w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2>labs</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://labs.play-with-k8s.com/\">https://labs.play-with-k8s.com/</a> 에서 가벼운 실험들 해볼 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>팁</h2>\n<p>자료들 찾아보니까 핵심은 다음 두 가지 같다.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>모의고사 익숙해지고 시간 내로 자신 있게 풀 수 있을 때까지 연습</li>\n<li>alias를 만들어서 자주 사용하는 명령어를 줄여서 사용</li>\n<li>documentation을 자주 보고 익숙해지기 + 미리 북마크해놓기</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>오늘의 풀이</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>A new application orange is deployed. There is something wrong with it. Identify and fix the issue.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>먼저 뭐가 문제인지 진단: <code>kubectl get pod orange</code></p>\n<p>보니까 LoopError이 뜨고 있음. 더 자세한 진단 확인: <code>kubectl describe pod orange</code></p>\n<p>이때 확인해본 결과:</p>\n<pre><code>Command:\n    sh\n    -c\n    sleeeep 2;\n</code></pre>\n<p>sleep에 오타 발견. 수정하기 위해: <code>kubectl edit pod orange</code></p>\n<p>수정을 하니까 오류가 엄청 많이 뜨는데, 아마 실행중인 pod를 수정하려 해서 그런듯. <code>kubectl delete pod orange</code>로 삭제하고 다시 yaml파일 생성하여 만들었다.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-yaml\">apiVersion: v1\nkind: Pod\nmetadata:\n    name: orange\nspec:\ninitContainers:\n  - name: init-myservice\n    image: busybox\n    command:\n    - sh\n    - -c\n    - sleep 2;\n  containers:\n  - name: orange-container\n    image: busybox:1.28\n    command:\n    - sh\n    - -c\n    - echo The app is running! &#x26;&#x26; sleep 3600\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>kubectl apply -f orange.yaml</code>로 다시 만들어주니까 정상적으로 생성되었다.</p>\n<h2>복기</h2>\n<p>문제 풀이 채점을 해보니 orange를 제외하고 다 맞았다. orange를 왜 틀렸는지 확인해보니, <code>kubectl edit pod orange</code>까진 맞는데, 이때 생성되는 temp파일으로 <code>kubectl replace -f /tmp/kubectl-edit-xxxx.yaml --force</code> 이런식으로 적용해줘야 했다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"d1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/4e897d725f678ca26f0dcf9381768b8c/5a190/d1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e897d725f678ca26f0dcf9381768b8c/772e8/d1.png 200w,\n/static/4e897d725f678ca26f0dcf9381768b8c/e17e5/d1.png 400w,\n/static/4e897d725f678ca26f0dcf9381768b8c/5a190/d1.png 800w,\n/static/4e897d725f678ca26f0dcf9381768b8c/84bf8/d1.png 1162w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>확실히 어려운 문제가 몇개 섞여있다.</p>\n<h3>자료</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://capgemini.github.io/kubernetes/Zero-to-CKA-in-2-Weeks/\">Zero to CKA in 2 Weeks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://hackernoon.com/how-to-pass-the-certified-kubernetes-administrator-exam-in-7-days-saw3uhu\">How to Pass the Certified Kubernetes Administrator Exam in 7 Days</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/alijahnas/CKA-practice-exercises?tab=readme-ov-file\">CKA-practice-exercises - Github</a></li>\n</ul>"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/kubernetes/CKA/cka2/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}